<span id="freeTextContainer4511141220477653987">I found this book to be very inspiring. It can be easy to get caught up in all of the negativity that surrounds us in life, but we need something to help to motivate us to keep moving forward with our lives. I am actually reading a page a day of this book and am finding it to help in my everyday life. I like the thoughts that are on each page and how they include a picture of a bird on a branch. By reading one thought a day, it&apos;s helping me to improve my outlook on life and become inspired to do</span>
  <span id="freeText4511141220477653987" style="display:none">I found this book to be very inspiring. It can be easy to get caught up in all of the negativity that surrounds us in life, but we need something to help to motivate us to keep moving forward with our lives. I am actually reading a page a day of this book and am finding it to help in my everyday life. I like the thoughts that are on each page and how they include a picture of a bird on a branch. By reading one thought a day, it's helping me to improve my outlook on life and become inspired to do great things. I would recommend this to others who want a more positive outlook on life. This book would be so helpful! It's already inspiring me daily.<br /><br /></span>
